Text: RE NDA GreenAsh CorporationI will review it over the weekend Vinh Nguyen GreenAsh Corporation wwwgreenashcom Original Message From mailto Sent Thursday February PM To Cc Subject NDA GreenAsh Corporation At the request of Paul Finken I am attaching our proposed form of NonDisclosure Agreement If the enclosed meets with your approval please execute the agreement and return it to me via fax no I will then have it executed by an officer of Enron If you have any comments or questions please do not hesitate to call me at or Mark Greenberg Senior Counsel at We look forward to hearing from you See attached file greenashdoc
